components.name: Load and Modify Station Data
components.description: Ingests stations.csv, parses installation_date, standardizes location names and converts the data to JSON. Uses the loadandmodify service (port 3003). Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Geocode Reconciliation
components.description: Geocodes station locations using the location field and adds latitude/longitude. Uses the reconciliation service (port 3003). Uses image default entrypoint/command.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful load and modify step

components.name: OpenMeteo Weather Data Extension
components.description: Adds historical weather variables based on geocoded latitude/longitude and installation_date. Uses the OpenMeteo service. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Land Use Classification Extension
components.description: Adds land use classification based on latitude/longitude using a GIS API. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Population Density Extension
components.description: Adds population density for the area surrounding each station location. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Environmental Risk Calculation
components.description: Computes custom environmental risk scores using precipitation, population density, and landuse type. Uses the columnextension service. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

components.name: Save Final Enriched Dataset
components.description: Exports the comprehensive environmental dataset to CSV. Uses the save service. Uses image default entrypoint/command.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after environmental risk calculation step
